<br>
Aeceus and Arixa caugh the scent as well and Aeceus turned to the other two wolves.<br>
&quot;We should attack now and kill them all.&quot;<br>
<br>
Arixa blinked and looked to him.<br>
&quot;We have our orders Aeceus, we can't danger Hippolyte's life more than it is.&quot;<br>
<br>
Alysia nodded.<br>
&quot;Scan the village more so, put two wolves secretly guardingt every hut. Put five along the back line of the weaponry hut. Send Scythe to watch over the hut they keep Hippolyte in.&quot;<br>
